              the moment.
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-bold">
                Here are some machine learning (ML) projects I'm developing ðŸ§ :
              </span>
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-row items-center justify-center">
              <a href="https://github.com/pjnalls/ml_projects" target="_blank">
                <Image
                  src={mlProjectsImage}
                  alt="image of a machine learning project"
                  loading="eager"
                  width={360}
                  height={360}
                />
              </a>
            </div>
            <br />
            <br />
